{
  "stem": "25348.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You would translate it as the white guardian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was my farewell from the kind Winklers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was just-- I can't remember whether New Year's Day or day after that I arrived in Hartha.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The place was called Hartha, spelled H-A-R-T-H-A, Hartha in Saxony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just walk in through the front entrance, and I was shouted down by the owner that this was not entrance for bloody Polacks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're not allowed to use the front entrance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] he called the cook to introduce me to the routine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The routine was, again, that's why I'm so good at peeling potatoes and vegetables.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And up to 11:00 or 12:00 or 1 o'clock, I don't know, till 2 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then my task was to clean the rooms upstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was all the guest rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The owner of this place was called Pabst, P-A-B-S-T.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Herr Pabst caught me at a crime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The light protruding from my door was-- I had stolen a newspaper from a wastebasket and reading it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some guest left the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came into the room-- which was fairly bear as it was-- removed the only bulb in the room and removed my blanket.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had a problem [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not-- you could wash in the dark, but you couldn't comb long hair, long plaits, in the dark.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So being an inventive brat, there was a guest's phone, telephone booth, and when you came into it, the light came on automatically.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it had some ad about pilsner beer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you could-- and I did, for a few days, my hair in that phone booth-- in that phone booth till Mr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pabst caught me again at this crime.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
